  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reinforce the rights of migrant youth in Oaxaca</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Every year, hundreds of children migrate with their families to agricultural fields and do not have access to regular schools. In the state of Oaxaca there are 47 migrant schools in indigenous communities that provide the children with the possibility to continue studying. Our project wants to reinforce their education by implementing workshops in order to teach the children about their rights.</narrative>
  </description>
